-- Italian Developer to Invest in Russian Resort, Vedomosti Says
-- B y   A n n a   S h i r y a e v s k a y a
-- 2012-07-23T04:20:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-23/italian-developer-to-invest-in-russian-resort-vedomosti-says.html
Rizzani de Eccher SpA, an Italian
developer, plans to invest about 1 billion euros ($1.2 billion)
in  Russia ’s OAO Northern Caucasus Resorts,  Vedomosti  reported
today, citing the operator of the ski, beach and spa resorts.  Rizzani de Eccher plans to build hotels and commercial
infrastructure in the southern Russian tourist region, the
newspaper said.  A protocol of intent between the two companies will be
signed today during Italian Prime Minister  Mario Monti ’s visit
to Russia, according to a Kremlin e-mailed statement yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anna Shiryaevskaya in Moscow at 
